---
description: Security, privacy, compliance, and tenant-isolation rules
alwaysApply: true
---

Treat message content as personal/confidential data.

Required:
- tenant isolation;
- least privilege;
- encrypted raw content and provider tokens;
- local redaction before external AI;
- fail closed on restricted or uncertain content;
- metadata-only logs;
- audited privileged actions;
- safe retention and deletion.

Before security-sensitive changes, read `docs/SECURITY_COMPLIANCE.md`.

Do not use real customer data in tests or fixtures.
Do not add a third-party processor without a vendor review and ADR.
